# {{ project_name }}

ReAct Agent template generated by `create-agent-app`.

## Template Overview

This template uses a ReAct loop with LangGraph:
- `reason_node` decides next action
- `tool_node` executes tool calls
- loop continues until no tool call remains

Included tools:
- `calculator` for safe arithmetic
- `web_search` for current information

## Architecture

```text
User Input
   |
   v
[reason_node] --tool call?--> [tool_node]
     ^                         |
     +-------------------------+
   no tool call
        |
        v
       END
```

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\\Scripts\\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env
python main.py
```

